{"tid":1877642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當裁員倒閉潮來臨， 就係考驗香港人有冇決心同勇氣既時候","createTime":"2020-02-13T06:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T10:20:50.000Z","uid":11454,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"96bb9a3667ed62fe84b2cf0a6bb44812988dd49a","tid":1877642,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:41:33.000Z","msg":"革命既引爆點<br />\n自古以來， 一係經濟下滑， 二係政治因數<br />\n8個月證明左香港人係第二點前提下， 好難成功<br />\n<br />\n經濟係最有可能引發全港上街既原因<br />\n因為冇野惡得過窮人<br />\n<br />\n但低技術， 口腔期廢中廢老太多<br />\n經濟崩盤時，甚至淺黃都會選擇跪同乞政府<br />\n變成同沙士後一樣， 有奶便事娘<br />\n<br />\n要時刻警惕03-19年， 香港既急速腐化<br />\n要有浴火重生既決心<br />\n無比既勇氣<br />\n先可以扭轉俾中共揸住春袋既日子"},{"pid":"4c3c593414171f2d9acbccb923186bde8e71c307","tid":1877642,"uid":126621,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"要中共狠心回血劍斬權貴<br />\n先救到經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則一齊收皮"},{"pid":"5c08b80983bc935ec5c8083a80183ce9017c675b","tid":1877642,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185cc1066254405b1793ce69b3c8ae1aae022cba","tid":1877642,"uid":258646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"到時港共會跪求開放全國自由行無限免簽證，迫爆香港，香港經濟復活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1da08e9d00c5741eba24b18e7971f955c9d91e2","tid":1877642,"uid":11454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"185cc1066254405b1793ce69b3c8ae1aae022cba","tid":1877642,"uid":258646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"到時港共會跪求開放全國自由行無限免簽證，迫爆香港，香港經濟復活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T07:00:53.000Z","msg":"預計一定會